    .merchant_info.col-sm-5.col-sm-offset-6
      .section
        .header SAVE 114% ON MERCHANT CASH ADVANCE
        .body
          We won’t lie to you, merchant cash advances suck because when you take one, you’re giving up your profits while paying it back. buynance™ increases your bottom line by 114% during the span of your merchant cash advance. We also shorten the amount of time it takes you to return to full profitability. Brokers and sales reps earn commissions – we don’t. They also charge junk fees and closing costs. We won’t.
