        .section.col-sm-9
          .header Tell Us About Your Business
          .body We just need to know the basics for now, no hardcore information is needed. Start the simple application and zip directly into step two.
      .start_auction.row
        .section.col-sm-8
          .header Start an Auction
          .body We take your business information and our Smart Match system matches that information with funders who are the best fit for you. You won’t be subject to a credit check until you select the offer that works for you. You remain firmly in control.
        .image.col-sm-4
          %img{src: "assets/auction.jpg"}/
      .get_funding.row
        .image.col-sm-4
          %img{src: "assets/funding.jpg"}/
        .section.col-sm-8
          .header GET FUNDING
          .body Once you select the offer that works best for you – you’ll be connected directly with your funding source and in most cases you will receive your commission free, junk fee free, business funding in as little as 3 days.
    .benefit
      .row
        .top_header Benefit
        .new_hr
          %img{src: "assets/line.jpg"}/
