          .body Shop with for the best deal from our hand selected list of top notch funders.
        .section.col-sm-2.drop
          .image
            %img{src: "assets/smart_match.jpg"}/
          .header Smart Match System
          .body Our smart match system helps to protect your profit margin during the life of your advance.
        .section.col-sm-2
          .image
            %img{src: "assets/credit_check.jpg"}/
          .header Only One Credit Check
          .body We protect you from excessive credit checks which harm your chances of getting more traditional funding later.
        .section.col-sm-2.drop
          .image
            %img{src: "assets/control.jpg"}/
          .header You Maintain Control
          .body You choose the funding source that best fits your needs without the high pressure sales tactics.
